task.summary: Re-design and removed the parser hander for IParserHandler(parse) function
Remove the IParser interface and de-couple it from the crawler class for better design
Big re-design to almost all of the classes. Added integration-test profile
Implement result abstract class to hold the result for the match, and added tests for it + refactoring.
Added delimiter as property and also to the constructor for each Result classes
huge refactoring and re-design for the skeleton of the app. Added new test cases and de-couple the result class from useless props. Added exceptions for match class

Huge refactoring. Replaced the SL4J logging instead of logback. Added Utils class for matches with equal operation. Removed the interface of ICrawler concept, because the crawler is very basic class and its the same for every case.
